                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18180401-106-off595 t18180401-106-crimeloc596"></join>, On the 10th of March, about three o'clock in the afternoon, a person came into my shop and asked if I was a pawnbroker? I said No; he immediately left; a man came in and said he had taken an umbrella. I then went out and secured the prisoner with it - He threw it away.</p>
               <p>
            
